.67億美元後，上季再錄虧損2,200萬美元，遠較去年同期的賺3.37億美元為差，部分原因是汽車保險商Geico的賠償成本增加，連同首季錄承銷虧損2.67億美元，連蝕2季；巴郡再保同樣受挫，主因受自然災害相關成本和會計開支影響。 <br />\n<br />\n巴郡上季投資收益亦由去年同期的3.94億美元，大減超過六成至1.43億美元，主要是去年同期因贖回卡夫亨氏優先股取得超過6億美元的一次過收益。相反，「鐵路王」BNSF上季盈利增長24%，至9.58億美元，反映該業務受惠於煤炭和其他貨運需求增長；巴郡能源的盈利亦按年升7%，至5.16億美元。 <br />\n<br />\n廢佬輸到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5610762527e382c4e5de2aae9d385b21eaa327","tid":571700,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"又話唔買科技股 ge ?"},{"pid":"83ccd3bf17adf88b48ef85c31f82ad73b0f4185b","tid":571700,"uid":158480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:49:50.000Z","msg":"連登吹水大賽開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ed22ca03f7e7e3dc3b30e9e86bcf341c58e8a4","tid":571700,"uid":18886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83ccd3bf17adf88b48ef85c31f82ad73b0f4185b","tid":571700,"uid":158480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:49:50.000Z","msg":"連登吹水大賽開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85184a50e69a3755e3104f0143f66a7a88a81576","tid":571700,"uid":93633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd5610762527e382c4e5de2aae9d385b21eaa327","tid":571700,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"又話唔買科技股 ge ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"Apple係巴郡已經係消費股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60b36669a9d7aacd44c8e99776d6b25800c0ecf5","tid":571700,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd5610762527e382c4e5de2aae9d385b21eaa327","tid":57170